com.microsoft.office.sfb.appsdk

Interface ConversationService

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Observable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AudioService, ChatService, VideoService

    public interface ConversationService
extends Observable
    This base interface defines common operations to control the local communications services (such as chat messaging, audio and video) that this endpoint provides into the conversation. The results of some operations on (sublcasses of) this interface may be visible in changes to (subclasses of) the ParticipantService belonging to the Conversation.getSelfParticipant()

    • Field Detail

      • CAN_START_PROPERTY_ID

        static final int CAN_START_PROPERTY_ID
        Property ID for notifying that internal state has changed and subscribers should check if the service can be started. Subscribers will be notified via the onPropertyChanged method on the Observable.OnPropertyChangedCallback interface with this property id. E.g. callback.onPropertyChanged(CAN_START_PROPERTY_ID). Clients are expected to call the canStart method in the callback to get the changed state.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • CAN_STOP_PROPERTY_ID

        static final int CAN_STOP_PROPERTY_ID
        Property ID for notifying that internal state has changed and subscribers should check if the service can be stopped. Subscribers will be notified via the onPropertyChanged method on the Observable.OnPropertyChangedCallback interface with this property id. E.g. callback.onPropertyChanged(CAN_STOP_PROPERTY_ID). Clients are expected to call the canStop method to get the changed state.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
